*3Ô∏è‚É£ Core Interview Topics & Questions*

*A. HTML/CSS*  
‚Ä¢ How does the box model work?  
‚Ä¢ Difference between `id` and `class`  
‚Ä¢ Flexbox vs Grid  

*B. JavaScript*  
‚Ä¢ What is hoisting?  
‚Ä¢ Difference between `var`, `let`, `const`  
‚Ä¢ Explain closures or event bubbling  

*C. React (if applicable)*  
‚Ä¢ What is a component?  
‚Ä¢ State vs Props  
‚Ä¢ What are hooks (useState, useEffect)?  

*D. Coding Rounds*  
‚Ä¢ Reverse a string  
‚Ä¢ FizzBuzz  
‚Ä¢ Find max/min in array  
‚Ä¢ Remove duplicates  

*E. Debugging + Tools*  
‚Ä¢ Use browser dev tools  
‚Ä¢ Console logging  
‚Ä¢ Understanding basic error messages  

