‚úÖ Projects to show:  
‚Ä¢ Responsive website  
‚Ä¢ To-do app  
‚Ä¢ Blog or portfolio site  
‚Ä¢ API-based app (e.g., weather, movie search)
‚úÖ Host on GitHub + Deploy via Netlify/Vercel  
‚úÖ Add README to explain project, tech stack, features

*5Ô∏è‚É£ Behavioral Questions*  
‚Ä¢ Why do you want to be a web developer?  
‚Ä¢ Tell me about a project you built.  
‚Ä¢ How do you handle bugs or challenges?

